        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " sense of both the second and third clauses is doubtful. Many renderings have been suggested; but it is not clear that any one of them is an improvement on the Authorised Version. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Thou shalt surely help with him",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The joint participation in an act of mercy towards a fallen beast would bring the enemies into friendly contact, and soften their feelings towards each other. Exodus 23:5",
        "children": []
